  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large skillet over medium high heat and cook the bacon lardon until crispy.",
    "Remove the bacon from the skillet and set aside, leaving the grease in the skillet.",
    "Add the lamb to the skillet and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, ginger, and garlic to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the tomato puree, yogurt, garam masala, cumin, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cooked bacon back into the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a scallop shell and cook on low in a slow cooker for 8 hours.",
    "Serve the lamb rogan josh hot, garnished with chopped cilantro if desired."
  ],
